                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="intro">
                <p>I'm a front-end developer & webdesigner who love creating websites, new design and coding! I'm curious and love sharing.
                <button class="btn-secondary"><a href="">contact me</a></button> if you want more information about my works</p>
